  "name": "RPlog_Celebration_of_Truth",
  "title": "Arrival for the Celebration of Truth",
  "summary": "The CDU ship Reannon Calder arrives at Trandosha, where the militant Trandoshans and the Seekers of the Truth have founded a new Theocratic Republic of Truth under High Priest Tantrix, hosting a week-long festival for galactic representatives. Aboard the command deck, Lt Commander Lynae Cassius briefs her hand-picked delegation, the eager Dug pilot Bakrak, the analytical droid HM743, and naval officer Sadim Gnik, on the warlike culture they are about to meet and the diplomatic care required. Landing at the bustling, heavily-secured Hsskhor starport amid bonfires, drums, and white-robed missionaries, the group presents credentials to a Trandoshan security squad. After verification, they are granted ambassadorial status and small-arms privileges and directed toward the White Citadel, with HM743 cheerfully testing the local droid's patience along the way.",
